《'''絕對小孩'''》，是[[朱德庸|朱德庸]]的[[四格漫画|四格漫画]]作品，於《[[中國時報|中國時報]]》親子版連載，是朱德庸唯一将视角对准“小孩”的漫画作品。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ent.163.com/12/0125/02/7OJ439C400032DGD.html|title=《绝对小孩》开展动漫秀|language=zh-cn|publisher=网易娱乐|author=|date=2006-02-08|accessdate=2015-02-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209161056/http://ent.163.com/12/0125/02/7OJ439C400032DGD.html|archive-date=2015-02-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>并有改编的同名[[舞台剧|舞台剧]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://epaper.jinghua.cn/html/2012-01/18/content_753478.htm|title=《绝对小孩》春节期间上演|language=zh-cn|publisher=京华时报·京华网|author=|date=2006-02-08|accessdate=2015-02-03|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150209160602/http://epaper.jinghua.cn/html/2012-01/18/content_753478.htm|archivedate=2015-02-09}}</ref>。作品诞生与朱德庸的儿子有关<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/j/2012-01-11/16383531207.shtml| title=中国儿艺《绝对小孩》春节上演|language=zh-cn|publisher=新浪网|author=|date=2006-02-08|accessdate=2015-02-03}}</ref>，改編[[舞台劇|舞台劇]]在[[中国儿童艺术剧院|中国儿童艺术剧院]]展演<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/j/2011-09-18/14503419681.shtml| title=中国儿艺排演朱德庸漫画改编剧《绝对小孩》|language=zh-cn|publisher=新浪网|author=|date=2006-02-08|accessdate=2015-02-03}}</ref>。在幽默中体现哲理<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://news.21cn.com/caiji/roll1/2011/09/17/9167529.shtml|title=朱德庸作品搬上儿童剧舞台 中国儿艺上演《绝对小孩》|language=zh-cn|publisher=滚动新闻|author=|date=2006-02-08|accessdate=2015-02-03|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216072250/http://news.21cn.com/caiji/roll1/2011/09/17/9167529.shtml|archivedate=2016-02-16|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

